## Section 2: Real-Time P&L

**Updates:** Every market data tick

### P&L Tracking

```python
class RealTimePnLTracker:
    async def on_market_data_tick(self, symbol: str, price: float):
        if symbol not in self.positions:
            return
        
        # Calculate unrealized P&L
        entry_price = self.cost_basis[symbol]
        position_pnl = (price - entry_price) * self.positions[symbol]
        self.unrealized_pnl = sum(self.position_pnl.values())
        
        # Track high/low
        total_pnl = self.realized_pnl + self.unrealized_pnl
        self.intraday_high = max(self.intraday_high, total_pnl)
        current_drawdown = total_pnl - self.intraday_high
        
        # Check circuit breakers
        await self._check_pnl_circuit_breakers(total_pnl, current_drawdown)
```

### P&L Attribution

```python
@dataclass
class PnLAttribution:
    total_pnl: float
    realized_pnl: float
    unrealized_pnl: float
    
    strategy_pnl: Dict[str, float]         # By strategy
    strategy_contribution: Dict[str, float] # As % of total
    position_pnl: Dict[str, float]         # By position
    
    top_contributors: List[Tuple[str, float]]
    bottom_contributors: List[Tuple[str, float]]
```

