## Section 3: Position Aging

**Schedule:** Hourly check, continuous monitoring

### Strategy-Specific Holding Limits

| Strategy Type | Max Holding |
|--------------|-------------|
| Arbitrage | 2 days |
| Mean Reversion | 3 days |
| Stat Arb | 5 days |
| Momentum | 7 days |
| Breakout | 10 days |
| Trend Following | 30 days |

### Age Categories

| Category | Age Ratio | Action |
|----------|-----------|--------|
| 🟢 FRESH | <50% | Normal operation |
| 🟡 AGING | 50-80% | Log warning |
| 🟠 STALE | 80-100% | Alert trader |
| 🔴 EXPIRED | >100% | Auto-close |

```python
async def _handle_expired_position(self, symbol, position_info, age):
    if self.auto_close_enabled:
        await self.risk_manager.close_position(
            symbol=symbol,
            reason='holding_period_exceeded',
            metadata={'age_days': age.days, 'strategy_id': position_info['strategy_id']}
        )
```

