## Section 6: Alerting & Monitoring

### Alert Thresholds

| Metric | Warning | Critical |
|--------|---------|----------|
| Daily P&L | -1.5% | -2% |
| Drawdown | -4% | -5% |
| Position Discrepancy | - | >$10K |
| Settlement Overdue | - | >24h |
| Order Failure Rate | - | >10% |

### Health Dashboard

```python
@dataclass
class SystemHealthStatus:
    overall_status: HealthLevel  # GREEN/YELLOW/RED/CRITICAL
    component_health: Dict[str, HealthLevel]
    
    positions_in_sync: bool
    working_orders_count: int
    pending_settlements_count: int
    daily_pnl: float
    current_drawdown: float
    
    active_alerts: List[Alert]
    recent_incidents: List[Incident]
```

### Health Levels

| Level | Status |
|-------|--------|
| 🟢 GREEN | All operational |
| 🟡 YELLOW | Minor issues |
| 🔴 RED | Significant issues |
| ⚫ CRITICAL | System failure |

