## Component Responsibility Matrix

| Component | Schedule | Modify Positions? | Authority |
|-----------|----------|-------------------|-----------|
| PositionReconciliation | 5 min | ⚠️ Auto-correct only | OPERATIONAL |
| RealTimePnLTracker | Every tick | ❌ READ-ONLY | OPERATIONAL |
| PositionAgingMonitor | Hourly | ⚠️ Auto-close only | OPERATIONAL |
| SettlementManager | Continuous | ❌ | OPERATIONAL |
| DisasterRecovery | 5 min | ✅ Recovery only | SYSTEM_CONTROL |
| AlertManager | Continuous | ❌ | OPERATIONAL |

---

## MANDATORY Requirements

1. **Reconciliation:** Sync with broker every 5 minutes
2. **P&L Tracking:** Update on every tick
3. **Position Aging:** Monitor against holding limits
4. **Settlement:** Track all trades through settlement
5. **State Persistence:** Snapshot every 5 minutes
6. **Health Monitoring:** Continuous checks
7. **Alerting:** Immediate on threshold breach

---

## PROHIBITED Patterns

| Pattern | Violation |
|---------|-----------|
| Ignoring discrepancies | Must track and resolve |
| Skipping reconciliation | Cannot be disabled |
| Stale P&L | Must update every tick |
| Untracked settlements | All trades need records |
| No backup | State must persist regularly |
| Silent failures | All failures must alert |

